    <item>
      <title>澳大利亚皇家的产量在与高生活成本的战斗中激增</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-28/aussie-real-yields-surge-in-battle-against-high-cost-of-living</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于政府宣布计划在选举年增加债务发行，以减轻对选民的生活压力，因此澳大利亚的通货膨胀调整后的债券收益率在十年来上升到了最高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-28/aussie-real-yields-surge-in-battle-against-high-cost-of-living</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 28 Mar 2025 03:39:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
